{
  "stem": "3012.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had an idea that we are somewhere up in the north.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that was all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Whether it was Poland or Czechoslovakia or Germany, we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't know where Auschwitz was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You are going to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's what they said.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we arrived in Parschnitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they put this up in-- it used to be probably a spinning factory or something to do with textiles.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because when you walked around, like when you went to the bathroom-- I mean, I'm again pushing it, because it was not a bathroom, it was a closed latrine, that's what it was-- you could see some machinery, that people told us, in the know, that they resemble the knitting factory machines.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They put us up in bunks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The lower bunk was shared by Mother and her sister.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the upper bunk I shared with a woman who got married to somebody from our town.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And from Parschnitz-- that was Czechoslovakia, German-occupied Czechoslovakia-- to a town about two kilometers far from there to Parschnitz, where we worked at heavy machinery at the AEG factory.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a munitions factory.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Trautenau.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "T-R-A-U-T-E-N-A-U, Trautenau.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this went on from August of '44 until liberation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then, of course worked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the work stopped before liberation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Mother eventually got well in Parschnitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a revier there, too, and just a little care.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Mother's wounds healed, and luckily, she made it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But then my aunt got very sick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was the same type of boil.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Whether it was lack of vitamin or food or both, we don't know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But the condition was mistreated by one of the nurses at the revier who didn't know anything about medical things.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
